@model ZLERP.Model.HR.HR_GZ_Welfare 
@section HeaderSection{
 
    <script src="@Url.Content("~/Scripts/Views/HR/HR_GZ_Welfare.js")" type="text/javascript" language="javascript"> </script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        var options = {
            storeUrl: '@Url.Action("Find")',
            SetUrl: '@Url.Action("Get", "HR_GZ_WelfareSet")',
            deptTreeUrl: '@Url.Action("FindTree", "Department")' 
        };
        $(function () {
            HR_GZ_WelfareIndexInit(options);
        });
    </script>
}
@*页面布局*@
<div id="Department" class="ztree" style="overflow: scroll;float: left; width: 12%">
</div>

<!-- 右边Grid -->
<div id="MyJqGrid" style="float: right; width: 87%">
</div>
<div id="MyFormDiv" class="mvcform" style="display: none;">
    @using (Html.BeginForm())
    {@Html.ValidationSummary()
        @Html.HiddenFor(m => m.ID )
        <table class="mvcform">
          <tr>  
            <td> 
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.PersonID)@Html.AutoComplete("PersonID", "PersonIDText", "Combo", "HR_Base_Personnel", "ID", "Name", "1=1", new { style = "width:120px" }) 
            </td>
             <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.SetID)@Html.DropDownListFor(m => m.SetID, (IEnumerable<SelectListItem>)ViewBag.SetID, "", new { @class = "text", style = "width:120px;" })
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
             <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.Cost)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.Cost)
            </td> 
        </tr>
        <tr> 
            <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.StartDate)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.StartDate,"date")
            </td> 
            <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.EndDate)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.EndDate, "date")
            </td>  
        </tr>
        <tr> 
             <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.IsStop)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.IsStop)
            </td> 
        </tr>
        <tr> 
            <td colspan="2">@Html.LabelFor(m => m.Remark)@Html.TextAreaFor(m => m.Remark, new { style = "width:70%" })
            </td>
        </tr> 
        </table>
    }
</div>
